-- Cowen Group Hires Thomas O'Mara to Expand Options, Convertibles Business
-- Jeff Kearns
-- 2010-06-28T20:01:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/cowen-group-hires-thomas-o-mara-to-expand-options-convertibles-business.html

          
          
             Cowen Group Inc., the New York-based
investment bank, said it hired Thomas O’Mara as head of equity
derivatives and convertibles.  
 O’Mara previously worked at Credit Suisse Group AG and
Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc., Cowen said today in a statement
sent by PR Newswire.  
